坡]]的[[猶大祭司|猶大祭司]]演唱會上作為支援嘉賓出演<ref>{{Cite news|title=Judas Priest brings firepower to Singapore, BABYMETAL makes its bid for future headlining show – gig report|date=2018-12-05}}</ref>，此外還出演[[澳洲|澳洲]]「{{link-ja|Good Things Festival|Good Things (Australian music festival)}} 2018」音樂節<ref name="cdjournal181223">{{Cite news|url=https://www.cdjournal.com/main/news/babymetal/81339|language=ja|script-title=ja:BABYMETALが豪ロック‧フェス〈Good Things 2018〉に出演　初の豪上陸にファン熱狂|newspaper=CDJournal|publisher=株式會社音樂出版社|date=2018-12-23|accessdate=2019-08-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://killyourstereo.com/news/1105088/melbourne-good-things-festival-the-big-review/|title=Melbourne Good Things Festival: The Big Review // Killyourstereo.com|accessdate=2018-12-23|website=Killyourstereo.com|language=en-AU}}</ref>。

